                    Postpaid Shared Internet Plans
                </div>
                <p>For the first time in Pakistan, Warid is offering you an  exciting way to share internet with two of your Warid friends and family  members, wherever they might be! So now avail Warid’s Shared Internet Plans and  enjoy mobile internet on smartphones, tablets or phablets with uninterrupted  internet browsing, surfing, online gaming and much more!</p>
                <p>The beauty of Warid’s Shared Internet Plans  is&nbsp;<strong>on-the-go utility</strong>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<strong>billing convenience</strong>! Not  only can you and two of your shared internet plan members enjoy internet  irrespective of each other’s location, but only the Shared Internet Plan  subscriber will be charged for the monthly plan! The secondary members will not  be charged for any internet usage as long as they are availing the allocated  shared internet limit.</p>
